title: NFL Free Agent QB Rankings: What will happen with Dak Prescott? Logical landing landing spots for Cam Newton, Ryan Fitzpatrick, Mitchell Trubisky and more (Football 2/24)
description:
There has been plenty of quarterback movement already this offseason with free agency still a few weeks away. That movement could continue with several notable quarterbacks set to hit the open market. Now Dak Prescott is in a class by himself and the Cowboys have to make a decision on his future at some point. On this episode, Ryan Wilson and John Breech break down the top 8 free agent QBs and their most logical landing spots. The guys focus on Jameis Winston, Cam Newton, Ryan Fitzpatrick, Mitchell Trubisky and of course, Andy Dalton. 
'Pick Six' is available on Apple Podcasts, Spotify, Stitcher, Google Podcasts, Castbox and wherever else you listen to podcasts.
